programme.title: World Watch: Forbidden History Ep3
programme.desc: Dokumentari bersama Jamie Theakson yang menyiasat mitos dan lagenda menarik dari sejarah. Jamie dan pasukan penyelidik merungkai misteri yang membentuk budaya masyarakat setempat. Episod kali ini memaparkan pengembaraan Jamie ke Jordan untuk menerokai bandar purba Petra yang pernah diduduki olah bangsa Nabbatean. Sehingga kini, hanya 20% tinggalan kota ini sudah digali, dan masih terdapat perbagai persoalan mengenai harta yang tertanam di dalam makam yang tersembunyi di kawasan ini.

programme.title: Bidadari: Mimpi Yang Sempurna Ep26
programme.desc: Wardah, pembantu kepada Haiman yang berwatak panas baran, berubah sikap selepas mendapat nasihat dan mereka menjadi rapat. Selepas lima tahun, Wardah bertemu Haiman semula dalam kes hak penjagaan anaknya. Ada surat dari Zaki di penjara untuk Wardah! Tapi, untuk apa? Kehadiran Adam melengkapi kehidupan Haiman dan Wardah. Bagaimana pula hubungan Wardah dengan Hakim? Pelakon: Aqasha, Tiz Zaqyah, Farahdhiya, Keith Foo, Elisha Sandha, Afifah Nasir, Shaharuddin Thamby, Arash Mohamad, Kuna, Aidil Aziz, Firdaus Ghufran, Rania Humaira, Jesse Lim, Ramli Salleh, dan Elanie Aidid.

programme.title: Cuit-Cuit: Misi Dania Cun (Siri 2) Ep11
programme.desc: Dania dipindahkan ke Hospital Sik, Kedah, dan menghadapi cabaran menyesuaikan diri dengan masyarakat setempat yang kritikal. Namun, sokongan daripada rakan sekerja seperti Dr. Amiran, Sister Jazmine, dan Jururawat Santesh membantunya melalui kesulitan di tempat baru. Semasa berjalan-jalan di kampung, Dania tersermpak dengan Taufik yang sedang melakonkan watak seorang askar. Orang kampung menganggap Taufik gila dan sering mempersendakannya, namun Dania ingin tampil membantu Taufik. Pelakon: Elyana Emrizal, Adeline Tsen, Shekeen Waida, Vigna Muthusamy, Nafiez Zaidi, Ziema Din, Man Khan, dan Dazrin Kamarudin.

programme.title: Citra: Dia Pengantinku Ep25
programme.desc: Aimi Najwa, seorang gadis yang lebih mementingkan kerjaya, terpaksa berhadapan dengan dua lelaki, Syed Ashraf, anak majikannya yang pernah dimarahinya, dan Shahabudin, teman zaman kanak-kanaknya. Walaupun keliru, Aimi Najwa mula menyedari perasaan cinta yang berkembang untuk kedua-duanya, dan kini dia harus memilih antara mereka. Aimi begitu marah dan menganggap bahawa Ashraff sengaja melukakan hatinya. Ashraff pula bermatian mengaku dia benar cintakan Aimi dan sudah berani melamar Aimi. Berjayakah Aimi menerima Ashraff kembali? Pelakon: Saharul Ridzwan, Mawar Rashid, Azriel Ismail, Tisha Shamsir, Catriona Ross, Azhar Amir, Esma Daniel, dan Liza Shahdan.

programme.desc: Aisya berkahwin dengan Danial atas pilihan keluarga, namun perkahwinan mereka terganggu akibat kehadiran Mila, teman rapat Danial. Setelah kehilangan anak, Danial memutuskan untuk berkahwin dengan Mila, sementara Aisya terpaksa menerima keputusan itu. Dalam episod ini Danial meminta pada Encik Hakim untuk mengurangkan skop kerja Aisha sementara dia mengandung. Pak Akub menasihati Danial supaya lebih berhati hati kerana ada orang mahu merosakan rumah tangga mereka. programme.title: Tamadun Yang Hilang Ep6
programme.desc: Dokumentari khas yang memaparkan sebuah pengembaraan ilmu sejarah Islam silam, satu tamadun yang hilang (Maghribi & Andalus). Secara retrospektifnya, Al Fadhil Ustaz Ezad Azraai Jamsari dan Prof Madya Dr Zamri Arifin (UKM) dijemput sebagai pakar rujuk bidang- berkaitan khazanah ilmu dan informasi berkaitan tamadun yang hilang di bumi Semenanjung Iberia (Sepanyol & Portugal). Saksikan tentang sejarah Kota Cordoba, Sepanyol yang merupakan kota termaju dan kota paling bercahaya pada abad itu.

programme.title: Ustaz Adik Cik
programme.desc: Elisa yang perlu menjaga dua anak saudaranya, Arif, 16 thn, dan Afik, 8 thn, ketika ibu bapa mereka pergi ke Mekah untuk tunaikan haji. Elisa yang selama ini berlagak baik di hadapan keluarga tapi sebenarnya seorang yang gemar bersosial, terpaksa menyesuaikan diri ketika menjaga Arif dan Afik. Sikap Arif yang suka bermain dan malas belajar, membuatkan Arif lebih rapat dan suka pada Elisa. Tetapi lain pula Afik yang lebih alim dan baik, sering persoalkan tindakan Elisa yang suka benarkan Arif bawa kawan-kawan datang ke rumah bermain sehingga abaikan solat dan kerja sekolah. Berbuih mulut Afik menasihati Arif dan Elisa tetapi mereka degil dan tetap malas hendak solat. Kerana tidak tahan melihat kemungkaran yang berlaku dalam rumah, Afik keluar untuk tenangkan jiwanya di masjid. Tetapi ketika itulah dia diculik oleh sekumpulan penjenayah dan ini membuat Arif dan Elisa rasa amat bersalah.

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

programme.title: Abang Lori Ohsem S1 Ep11
programme.desc: Nek Wan kritikal dan dimasukkan ke hospital. Lufia datang hanya ingin melawat Nek Wan. Dalam pada tu, Luqman masih meraih kepercayaan Lufia. Dani mengaku pada Luqman yang memang dia musnahkan hubungan Luqman dan Lufia. Luqman cuba memberitahu Lufia yang Dani sebenarnya sabotaj mereka, namun Lufia langsung tidak percaya. Dani pula mengambil kesempatan, berbuat baik dan cuba untuk mencuri hati Lufia. Lufia makin melayan kehadiran Dani, namun jauh disudut hatinya dia merindui Luqman dan timbul rasa cemburu dalam dirinya apabila melihat Chery begitu caring dan rapat dengan Luqman, makin bertambah benci Lufia pada Luqman. Pergaduhan Luqman dan Lufia semakin melarat sehingga Lufia sanggup menghina kerjaya Luqman sebagai pemandu lori. Ini semua disebabkan Dani mula berjaya meracuni fikiran Lufia.

Mereka akhirnya berkahwin dan mendapat restu keluarga, membuktikan cinta sejati mereka mampu bertahan walaupun diuji pelbagai cabaran.

programme.title: 11 Cinta Sebelum Kamu
programme.desc: Ray, selepas melamar Khadeja, Ray bertemu bakal ibu mentuanya, Dato' Shikin, seorang ibu tunggal dan peguam terkenal. Tanpa mengetahui latar belakang keluarga Khadeja, Ray mendapati bahawa Dato' Shikin telah menyelidik kehidupan masa lalunya yang 'nakal. Demi mendapatkan restu bagi mengahwini Khadeja, Dato Shikin telah menetapkan satu syarat, Ray perlu berdepan dan meminta maaf kepada kesemua 11 bekas teman wanitanya, merakam setiap kemaafan yang diberikan kepada Ray, dan menghantarnya kepada Dato' Shikin dalam tempoh 30 hari. Terdesak, Ray bersetuju dengan syarat tersebut dan meminta bantuan rakan baiknya, Kamil. Misi menjadi rumit apabila Ray dan Kamil mendapati bekas-bekas teman wanitanya, pesakit mental, jurulatih MMA, pegawai polis narkotik, barista kafe, penjaga zoo, pengusaha makanan dan pelbagai lagi, kesemuanya masih marah dengan Ray, terutamanya Aisha, kenalan rapat Ray dari bangku sekolah yang juga kononnya salah seorang dari 11 orang bekas kekasih Ray. Kali terakhir Ray bertemu dengan Aisha adalah 13 tahun lepas. Aisha menyedari bahawa Ray benar-benar telah berubah dan memutuskan untuk membantu Ray menyelesaikan misinya. Ray dan Aisha secara tidak diduga mula jatuh hati antara satu sama lain. Perasaan yang sama dirasai mereka 13 tahun lepas namun dipendam sehingga kini. Tanpa pengetahuan Ray, Dato' Shikin telah mengupah seseorang yang rapat dengan Ray untuk menggagalkan misinya. Masa 30 hari kian hampir tamat, dan Aisha merupakan orang yang terakhir dalam misi Ray untuk memohon kemaafan

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep7
programme.desc: Riadi membawa anak-anak dan Suhana ke pulau. Mereka tersesat di hutan semasa jungle tracking.Apabila malam, setiap pokok di hutan tu dipenuhi dengan buaian tergantung serta nyanyian lagu Buai laju-laju yang mengasyikkan di pendengaran mereka. Mereka mencari empunya suara tetapi tidak di jumpai sehingga mereka ketiduran. Kelihatan wanita cantik dan separuh jembalang memerhati mereka yang sedang tidur.

programme.title: Kapsul
programme.desc: Kapsul masa wawasan 2020 yang ditanam oleh Tun Dr. Mahathir Mohamad telah dicuri dan membawa Zohri kembali ke masa lalu. Zohri kini terperangkap di tengah-tengah pergolakan bangsa Melayu untuk mencapai kemerdekaan dan membawa bangsa Melayu keluar dari belenggu kemiskinan. Zohri melihat dan merasai sendiri erti perjuangan umatnya yang tidak pernah dibayangkannya selama ini. Dia lihat, dia rasa dan kini dia mula faham betapa peritnya liku-liku sejarah negara dan bangsa. Perjalanan Zohri berterusan dari satu zaman ke satu zaman dan tiada siapa yang dapat mengembalikannya ke zamannya melainkan dirinya sendiri.

programme.title: Sosok Ketiga
programme.desc: Apabila Nuri menerima Yuni yang merupakan sahabat baiknya, sebagai madunya, dia mencetuskan siri supernatural dan konflik mendalam bagi memenangi semula cinta hati suaminya.

programme.title: Khun Pan
programme.desc: Cerita ini mengisahkan tentang seorang pegawai polis bernama Khun Phan dalam Perang Dunia Kedua. Dia menjalankan misi penyamaran untuk menumpaskan seorang gabenor di sebuah pulau yang semua orang di sana dianggap penyamun.

programme.title: Encounter
programme.desc: Sekumpulan rakan mendedahkan objek dunia lain di padang luar bandar yang mereka temui menyimpan rahsia yang lebih besar daripada yang mereka bayangkan.

programme.title: Plan B Ep10
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai, Iris, Mika dan Que terlibat dalam satu rompakan. Mereka merompak sebuah van syarikat keselamatan milik bapa Mika, Yusof, yang membawa sejumlah wang besar. Mereka bertembung dengan kumpulan yang diketuai oleh King. Dalam aksi tembak menembak antara kedua-dua kumpulan, kesemua pengawal keselamatan yang mengiringi wang itu, ditembak mati oleh King. Mika juga cedera ditembak. Dalam aksi kejar mengejar antara dua kumpulan itu dan tembak menembak, King dan orang-orangnya mati ditembak oleh Khai, ketika berjaya membawa lari wang rompakan itu. Di pejabat keselamatan, Yusof dapat menyaksi aksi rompakan itu melalui kamera tertutup dan mendapati anaknya, Mika ditembak.

programme.title: Sosok Ketiga

programme.title: Evolusi KL Drift
programme.desc: Zack dan Sham adalah dua nama yang sinonim dengan istilah keakraban. Hubungan sebagai dua sahabat karib yang sama-sama berkongsi hobi dan minat dalam bidang perlumbaan kereta 'drift'.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. Apabila Rachel mula mengalami halusinasi mengenai ibu mereka yang sudah meninggal dan sesuatu artifak purba, petunjuk-petunjuk menakutkan mula terbongkar mengenai masa lalu keluarga mereka.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep4
programme.desc: Hariz yakin Budi ada kena mengena kerana Budi ada masa dia bertengkar dengan Andy, Hariz tahu Budi adalah peminatnya, mungkin peminat ini bunuh mereka yang cuba sakiti Hariz.

programme.title: Taken
programme.desc: Seorang ejen CIA yang telah bersara mengembara merentasi Eropah dan menggunakan kemahiran lamanya untuk menyelamatkan anak perempuannya yang telah lama terpisah, yang diculik semasa dalam perjalanan ke Paris.

programme.title: Awoken
programme.desc: Apabila tiada apa yang boleh dilakukan untuk pesakit Insomnia Fatal Familial di hospital, seorang pelajar perubatan telah menyuruh abangnya dipindahkan ke kemudahan rahsia di ruang bawah tanah untuk rawatan alternatif.

programme.title: The Hollow One
programme.desc: Rachel dan Anna pulang ke rumah dua tahun selepas kematian ibu mereka, dan dapati bandar itu ditinggalkan dengan rumah mereka dalam keadaan kacau dan kotor. programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep7
programme.desc: Riadi membawa anak-anak dan Suhana ke pulau. Mereka tersesat di hutan semasa jungle tracking.Apabila malam, setiap pokok di hutan tu dipenuhi dengan buaian tergantung serta nyanyian lagu Buai laju-laju yang mengasyikkan di pendengaran mereka. Mereka mencari empunya suara tetapi tidak di jumpai sehingga mereka ketiduran. Kelihatan wanita cantik dan separuh jembalang memerhati mereka yang sedang tidur.

programme.title: Din Tiger Ep7
programme.desc: Tan Sri Alif menghadapi krisis akibat kesilapan Anat yang semakin merumitkan operasi, ini menyebabkan Lai Chee berasa kecewa dan marah, dibelenggu dengan konflik emosi.

programme.title: Jailangkung Sandekala
programme.desc: Keganasan ghaib berpusat pada sebuah keluarga kecil yang terdiri daripada Adrian dan isterinya Sandra, bersama dua anak mereka, Niki dan Kinan, yang sedang bercuti ke luar bandar.

programme.title: Gemersik Berbisik Ep7
programme.desc: Riadi membawa anak-anak dan Suhana ke pulau. Mereka tersesat di hutan semasa jungle tracking.Apabila malam, setiap pokok di hutan tu dipenuhi dengan buaian tergantung serta nyanyian lagu Buai laju-laju yang mengasyikkan di pendengaran mereka. Mereka mencari empunya suara tetapi tidak di jumpai sehingga mereka ketiduran. Kelihatan wanita cantik dan separuh jembalang memerhati mereka yang sedang tidur.

programme.title: Sebelum Titik Noktah Ep2
programme.desc: Amelia simpan rahsia bahawa dia bertengkar dengan Amer di dalam hutan dan dia yang tolak Amer jatuh, dia fikir dia yang sebabkan kematian tunangnya itu. Namun bila Amelia dapat tahu tentang ada kesan seolah diikat leher Amer. Dia pula mengesyaki Hariz, kerana Amelia yakin ada orang lain di hutan itu.

programme.title: Hatchet 3
programme.desc: Pasukan mencari dan pemulihan menuju ke paya berhantu Victor Crowley untuk mengambil kepingan itu, dan Marybeth mengetahui rahsia untuk menamatkan sumpahan voodoo yang telah menyebabkan Victor Crowley mengganas Paya Pulau Madu selama beberapa dekad.

programme.title: Puteri Impian 2
programme.desc: Gadis kilang yang menolak lamaran seorang kerabat diraja Tengku Faizal, menaruh hati terhadap jurukamera stesen televisyen, Zul. Nora menyukai Zul tetapi dia telah pun menjalin hubungan bersama Lisa. Adik kepada Tengku Faizal, Tengku Farid ingin membawa semula Nora kembali ke abangnya. Tekad, dia ingin mengangkat semula maruah abangnya.

programme.title: Cinta U-Turn
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Faiz, seorang anak lelaki kepada ahli perniagaan bernama Datuk Shuib yang ingin dijodohkan dengan Juliana. Kekeliruan mula berlaku apabila gambar Juliana telah bertukar dengan gambar orang lain yang tidak menepati citrasa Faiz. Dia melarikan diri dan berkenalan dengan Hafiz. Mereka bersama-sama bekerja di sebuah bengkel. Pada suatu hari, Juliana datang ke bengkel itu dan telah membuatkan Faiz jatuh cinta padanya. Keadaan menjadi huru hara apabila berlakunya penyamaran antara Faiz dan Hafiz dalam memenangi hati bapa Juliana, iaitu Datuk Jamal.

programme.title: Ali Setan 2
programme.desc: Ikatan yang ingin tercipta terpaksa dileraikan kerana campur tangan keluarga menyebabkan Ali dan Asmidar pergi membawa haluan sendiri. Rancangan untuk mendirikan rumahtangga telah diganggu oleh Jeff yang inginkan Asmidar. Ayah Asmidar pula menyuruhnya berkahwin bersama Jeff - namun setelah beberapa bulan mereka pun bercerai kerana tidak bahagia. Ali dan Asmidar pun bersatu semula.

programme.title: Cinta Bollywood
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Shahrul, anak Tok Penghulu merangkap seorang penganggur yang tinggal di Parit Buntar bersama keluarganya. Dia menaruh hati kepada seorang gadis bernama Asha. Pada suatu hari, seorang penerbit filem telah datang ke kampungnya untuk membuat penggambaran drama berjudul Cinta Bollywood. Shahrul kemudiannya dilantik menjadi production manager dan pelakon untuk penggambaran drama itu. Ketika penggambaran dibuat, Salman, hero drama itu semakin rapat dengan Asha dan hal ini membuatkan Shahrul cemburu.

programme.title: Cikgu Romantik
programme.desc: Bercita-cita ingin menjadi selebriti terkenal, Azizah mendapat surat uji bakat yang bertempat di Kuala Lumpur. Dia pun pergi dan menetap di rumah temannya, Tila lalu berkenalan bersama seorang guru vokal iaitu Ramli. Muncul pula Shahrul yang mengatakan bahawa raut wajah Azizah seiras dengan isterinya yang telah meninggal dunia.

programme.title: Bila Dah Sayang
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Kamarudin yang tak jadi bertunang dengan Tengku Suraya kerana kekasihnya itu masih belum bersedia untuk berkahwin. Dalam hati mereka masih ada perasaan sayang antara satu sama lain walaupun mereka sering bertengkar. Namun berlaku satu insiden yang membuatkan Kamarudin terpikat dengan seorang gadis Cina bernama Miss Yap.

programme.title: Ali Setan
programme.desc: Ali pelajar universiti yang nakal dan suka bergurau berjumpa Asmidar ketika dalam perjalanan ke universiti. Ali selalu mencari jalan untuk mengusik Asmidar, lama kelamaan perasaan cinta mula berputik antara mereka berdua. Konflik mula terjadi apabila Ali sebenarnya sudah berkahwin dengan Tipah namun atas sebab terpaksa.

programme.title: Kasih Farra
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Farra yang bercinta dengan Lokman, seorang lelaki yang jauh lebih tua daripada usianya. Lokman baru pulang ke Malaysia selepas lebih 20 tahun merantau ke luar negara. Tanpa pengetahuan Lokman, Farra ialah anak kepada bekas kekasihnya, Zura. Dalam masa yang sama, Zura sedang mencari Lokman untuk meminta maaf atas apa yang berlaku kepada hubungan mereka di masa lampau.

programme.title: Puteri Impian
programme.desc: Pekerja kilang, Puteri Nora sentiasa mengimpikan untuk menjadi seorang puteri raja. Impiannya menjadi kenyataan apabila dia diterima menyertai pertandingan "Memburu Impian". Kehidupannya berubah sekelip mata apabila bertemu Tengku Faizal, seorang putera raja. Namun, Zul, jurukameranya dalam rancangan itu turut menyukai Puteri Nora. Pilihan harus dibuat antara kemewahan atau kebebasan.

programme.title: Nylea & Harris
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Harris yang terpaksa bekerja sebagai pelayan walaupun dia memiliki kelulusan tinggi. Dia kemudiannya berjaya mendapat kerja sebagai arkitek di sebuah firma milik Tan Sri Kadir. Tugas pertama Harris ialah untuk menyiapkan sebuah rumah untuk anak perempuan Tan Sri Kadir iaitu Nylea. Pada mulanya Harris dan Nylea sering bertengkar namun lama kelamaan timbul bibit-bibit percintaan antara mereka berdua. Walau bagaimanapun, muncul pula Chris, bekas tunangan Nylea ke dalam hidup mereka yang membuatkan Harris sangat kecewa.

programme.title: (L) TVS Tengahari S EpL
programme.desc: TVS Tengahari presents a comprehensive look at domestic and international news stories, providing viewers with an in-depth understanding of current affairs during the midday broadcast.

programme.title: Weaving And Craft S Ep1
programme.desc: Exploring the vibrant world of traditional handicrafts and textiles, showcasing the living culture, identity, and heritage within Sarawak's rich diversity.

programme.title: Paradoks S1 Ep7
programme.desc: Zainal Nuruddin, pemilik studio rakaman, kagum dengan muzik kugiran kaki lima, lalu bekerjasama dengan Ali Zayn, pemuda misteri yang rupanya Pengembara Masa. Cinta Ali pada anak Zainal, Syaheera, mencetus dilema besar.

programme.title: Maaf Dari Khilaf
programme.desc: Hasrat Bakar dan Salimah untuk memiliki zuriat tidak kesampaian apabila Salimah mengalami keguguran. Dia tekad untuk mencari angkara siapa yang mencampak sampah dari tingkat atas rumah flatnya yang mengakibatkan keguguran kandungan isterinya. Pada masa yang sama, jiran mereka Rosnah berasa amat bersalah kerana dia tahu ini semua adalah salahnya.

programme.title: Missing You

programme.title: Senjakala Di Manado
programme.desc: Johny WW Lengkong (Ray Sahetapy), seorang pelaut yang telah meninggalkan keluarganya selama hampir 20 tahun, berniat kembali ke Manado dengan harapan keluarganya mau memaafkannya. Namun ternyata istrinya telah meninggal dunia dan meninggalkan seorang anak bernama Pingkan (Mikha Tambayong). Johny pun berjanji akan merawat Pingkan, tetapi ternyata semua tidak berjalan dengan mudah. Pingkan merasa terganggu tatkala Johny mulai mencampuri urusan asmaranya dengan Brando (Fero Walandouw), kekasihnya, lantaran Johny merasa Brando bukan pria baik-baik. programme.title: Jatim Traveler Ep7
programme.desc: Jatim Traveler membawa anda mengembara menerokai keunikan kulinari, keindahan destinasi pelancongan, dan tradisi istimewa di serata pelosok Jawa Timur.

programme.title: My Love My Oppa Batagor Haseyo
programme.desc: Apa yang terjadi apabila orang yang melanggar Wulan merupakan idolanya, David. Wulan juga berpeluang menjadi pembantu peribadi David.

programme.title: Semarak Indosiar 2021 Ep27
programme.desc: Kemeriahan pentas Indosiar tetap hadir dengan keindahan budaya Indonesia dalam rancangan Indosiar Semarak 2021. Iringi malam anda dengan persembahan yang menakjubkan daripada artis serta penyanyi dari ibu kota.

programme.title: Cinta Setelah Cinta S2 Ep47
programme.desc: Starla menyangka dia telah menghadapi segalanya, tetapi penipuan Niko jauh lebih mendalam daripada yang disangkanya. Ketika dia terus berusaha mempertahankan perkahwinannya, ancaman baharu muncul. Ayu, yang masih taksub dengan Niko, semakin mengikatnya dalam perangkap dengan menggunakan anak mereka yang belum lahir sebagai umpan. Pada masa yang sama, naluri Starla merasakan ada sesuatu yang tidak kena, dan dia mula diburu oleh bayang-bayang serta rahsia gelap. Dengan keluarganya di ambang bahaya dan emosinya semakin tertekan, adakah Starla mampu melindungi orang-orang tersayang? Atau adakah pengkhianatan Niko akan mendorongnya melangkaui batas yang tidakbolehkembali?

Although Siou-Ying was betrayed by You-Tsai, she has still been a dutiful daughter to her mother-in-law, and has single-mindedly raised four children.

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa (T) Ep262
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: The Tradition Story of Taiwan (T) Ep5050
programme.desc: The Tradition Story of Taiwan presents a series of tales and folktales in Taiwan that have been pass down from one generation to another generation.

programme.title: Echoes of the Thunder
programme.desc: Two half-brothers, Nam and Fire, are top racing drivers. In a racing challenge with Japanese driver Kenji, Nam causes a young racing driver to be seriously injured and is depressed. Fire stands up for Nam and decides to compete with Kenji in an illegal street car race. Who will win the race? Can Nam finally bounce back?

programme.title: My Wife is a Gambling Maestro
programme.desc: Natalie Yao Meng stars as the gambling queen, Ying Ying, who is a contender for the Asian God of Gamblers competition. But before the competition she is betrayed by her fianc and left for dead. Rescued by a young man called Gerrard, who suffering from amnesia, Ying Ying, must recover in time to compete in the big event!

programme.title: Look Up
programme.desc: This film celebrates the 25th anniversary of Hong Kongs Handover in a series of four cultural stories about young Hong Kongers from different walks of life: a young man with autism pursuing his dream, a reconciliation between father and son, a Chinese opera star helping young pop singers, and a Nepali youth becoming a professional lion dancer.

programme.title: The Eagle Shooting Heroes
programme.desc: Executive produced by Wong Kar Wai, The Eagle Shooting Heroes is loosely based on Louis Chas classics. Whilst mistaken identity and rampant gender confusion are on the menu, Sammo Hungs action direction and the incredible all-star casts also keep the laughs and thrills coming in this Hong Kong-style crazy comedy.

programme.title: One and Only
programme.desc: Veteran street dancer Ding Lei, invites passionate street dancer, Chen Shuo to his dance club. Sparks fly when Chen dances with the clubs top dancers. Chen pursues his dream to perform but discovers that Ding has invited him for another reason. As both of them deal with hard times, can they turn the tide on the challenges that they are facing?

programme.title: Heroic Duo
programme.desc: Police officer Ken needs help to solve a grisly crime that the offender has no recollection of committing. Ken seeks out Jack, a former psychologist who is now imprisoned. Forming an uneasy truce, this unconventional duo sets out to find the man responsible. It is at this time that Ken falls into a trap set up by Jack

programme.title: Hello Stranger
programme.desc: This is a Thai romantic comedy. The story portrays a young Thai man and woman who meet by coincidence while on vacation in South Korea. They decide to tour the country together while keeping their names a secret from each other. From unwillingly at first, then become best friends and fall in love finally.

programme.title: S Storm
programme.desc: ICAC Chief Officer Luk witnesses a suspects murder while investigating an illegal soccer gambling case, but is unable to disclose information to Chief Inspector Lau due to his code of confidentiality, thereby hindering Laus investigation. While starting the case with mutual distrust, they end up reaching a rapport to uproot the crime syndicate.

programme.title: I'm Livin' It
programme.desc: Once a successful banker, Bowen now spends his nights in a 24-hour fast food joint where he meets a group of homeless people. Together they strive to get themselves out of rock bottom.

programme.title: American Dreams in China
programme.desc: During the economic reform period in the 80s, three undergraduates are brought together by a common ambition to live the American dream.

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Set in 2020 during the outbreak of COVID-19, the movie features interconnected stories of three women's lives as they navigate the uncertain future amongst their respective friends and families. From the struggles at home to challenges in relationships and conflicts at work, these three women rise with strength when faced with plights unknown.

programme.title: Everything Under Control
programme.desc: During a diamond heist, one of the security escorts, Jelly, steals the diamonds and flees. Fellow security escorts, Yau Shing and Penguin, are forced to help the robber track down the diamonds. They stumble onto a remote village along the way, encountering strange villagers and mysterious incidents. Can they finally locate Jelly and the diamonds?

programme.title: My Kickass Wife
programme.desc: Jade is a beautiful royal guard who is set up for marriage by the Queen in order to avoid the King setting eyes on her. Jade falls for Sean and helps him win the contest for her. After the wedding, Sean discovers her bad temper and visits a brothel in his despair. He meets and is attracted to a girl there, not knowing she has a secret agenda...

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Men Suddenly in Love
programme.desc: Five high-school alumni - councilor Ng Yuk Yan, actor Cheung Chau Wan, gynecologist Fu Mo Sum, feng shui master Szeto Kei Fung, and dance coach Charlie Lam - get together to throw a birthday party for their respected teacher Mr. Chu, who enlightened them about the birds and the bees. Five delectable young models appear at the party, during which the 80-year-old educator gets too excited and unfortunately kicks the bucket - but not before telling his pupils to fulfill his last wish and get a little naughty! The quintet of married men then takes it upon themselves to conquer the babes, all the while trying to evade the watchful eye of their wives.

programme.title: Operation Bangkok
programme.desc: A military veteran, Wu Wei and an undercover cop, Tian Ming lead a team to rescue the hostages captured by a band of thugs in an island outside of Bangkok. As they are about to leave after the rescue, Wu finds that his daughter is also kidnapped, and decides to stay on with Ming to fight the thugs and save her.

programme.title: Death Stranding
programme.desc: To overhaul the underground gambling industry, the police join hands with the gambling association to crack down on illegal casinos. They auction off new casino licenses to regulate the industry, but this results in an upheaval in the gambling world, unveiling the hidden interests and secrets while sparking conflicts between gangs...

programme.title: Cloudy Mountain
programme.desc: When a decade-long tunnel project is about to complete, an earthquake strikes and leads to a series of subsidence and landslides. The tunnel and a nearby town are at stake. A retired soldier and his son step up to try and stop the disasters at source. Will the authority decide to blow up the tunnel to save the 160,000 people in town?

programme.title: Night and Fog
programme.desc: Following The Way We Are, this is based on a true story happening in Tin Shui Wai. It revolves around an older, unemployed Hong Kong man, his young Mainland wife and their two daughters. Their lives, unfortunately, are anything but easy, and the shocking conclusion raises issues about the plight of the socially deprived lower class.

programme.title: Love Punch
programme.desc: Talented boxer Jia Yang is caught in an underground fight to clear her father's debts. She loses her Olympic aspiration and vanishes from the boxing world. 10 years later, Coach Li Yue is determined to help her honour her father's wish by returning to the ring. As passion and obligation collide, can Jia Yang revive her abandoned boxing dream?

programme.title: The Rookies
programme.desc: An extreme sports lover accidentally gets involved in an illegal trading activity by international crime syndicates. Led by international special agent Bruce, he forms an amateur unit with a police officer, an inventor and a doctor to fight the crime syndicates together, leading to a series of thrilling and hilarious adventures.

programme.title: Princess and 7 Kung Fu Masters
programme.desc: Seven Kung Fu masters live in Lucky Town, the only safe residing place in northeast China. When warlord Lam refuses to side with the Japanese, an agent is assigned to take over his army and kill his daughter using ninjutsu. Lams daughter escapes and seeks help from the seven masters, who finally defeat the enemy and save the warlord!

programme.title: Marriage With A Liar
programme.desc: Kiki and her boyfriend of seven years, Sean, are to be married in a week but both cheated on each other three days before the wedding. Faced with each of their perfect partners, Kiki and Sean ignore their responsibilities to each other and choose to go their separate ways

programme.title: Far Far Away
programme.desc: A 28-year-old IT geek has only been in love once. Surprisingly, he ends up getting romantically involved with five different women this year and the one thing they have in common is that they all live in far flung areas of Hong Kong. After taking five intensive relationship courses within these 365 days, will he find the-one?

programme.title: Maoshan Heavenly Master
programme.desc: Prisoner Chi flees away under Master Zhangs custody, causing the latter to be expelled from his clan. On his way to find Chi, Master Zhang arrives at a place where many people vanish for no reason. He soon discovers that it is Chi who captures them in his training to become a serpent demon. The war between human and demon has just begun!

programme.title: Article 20
programme.desc: Han Ming, a prosecutor, faces a whirlwind of complications in his work and family lives: his son's clash with another student in school and his wife's intervention, as well as the strained partnerships at work. Amidst it all, a critical case challenges his sense of righteousness, and he decides to gamble everything to seek fairness and justice.

programme.title: Protege
programme.desc: Undercover Police Nick has spent 8 years working for the drug baron Quin, so as to collect evidence of his drug trafficking activities. After gaining Quins trust, Nick becomes his protg and succeeds him as the drug baron when Quin retires. However, Nick has lost himself in his split life between trading drugs and searching for criminal evidence.

programme.title: PTU
programme.desc: When OCTB (Organized Crime And Triad Bureau) officer, Sergeant Lo Sa, loses his police revolver to four triad young thugs, he seeks help from Sergeant Mike Ho of the PTU (Police Tactical Unit) to find his lost revolver. Ho and his patrolling PTU team has until dawn to recover the gun and clean up the mess.

programme.title: The Invisible Guest
programme.desc: Young and beautiful entrepreneur Joanna is a prime suspect in a locked-room murder where her lover is found dead. She pays off a police officer to prove her innocence. During the investigation, they discover another murder case involving Joanna and her lover, and eventually reveals the truth.

programme.title: Echoes of the Rainbow
programme.desc: Set in Hong Kong in the 1960s, the story revolves around the family of a hardworking shoemaker Mr Law, with his happy-go-lucky wife and two sons a talented elder son and an eight-year-old eccentric younger son. While their lives are not always smooth-sailing, the family sticks together and support one another through thick and thin.

programme.title: The Ex-Files 4: Marriage Plan
programme.desc: Two brothers, Meng Yun and Yu Fei, are of marriageable age and are facing challenges in love. Yun dodges family pressure to marry after his breakup, while Fei and his girlfriend opt for a marriage cooling-off period to tackle marriage issues.

programme.title: Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons
programme.desc: The sequel to "Journey to the West: Conquering the Demons", this happens after Monkey King has gained enlightenment and is Tang San Zang's disciple. Tang, Monkey King, Sandy and Pigsy continue their journey to the West, where they have to fight and eliminate demons while dealing with their own changes, putting their bond to the test.

programme.title: Let It Ghost
programme.desc: The movie consists of three urban ghost stories: when a film crew is haunted by a ghost, the director decides to cast her to play the ghost; when a taxi driver takes his girlfriend to a staycation, a horny ghost adds spice to it; a wandering child ghost refuses to leave a mall that is to be demolished, so the tenants help her to move on.

programme.title: What Price Honesty
programme.desc: In this period martial arts thriller, three police graduates are assigned to a town rife with crimes and corruption. They vow to uphold justice but are hampered by their corrupt superior, resulting in them putting their lives and the lives of their beloved in danger.

programme.title: The Cave of Silken Web
programme.desc: In this third instalment of Shaw Brothers Journey to the West, Monk Tang San Zang is trapped by seven seductive spider spirits who are hell-bent on achieving immortality by eating him! Monkey, Pigsy and Sha Wu Jing have to fight the spider spirits to rescue Monk Tang San Zang.

programme.title: Wits Of The Brats
programme.desc: Tou Kuan is a wealthy Kwangtung brat with a good kung fu background, he has only one ambition: to pit his wits against three shady masters of the North. The first, conman Che Tsai. The second, a professional romantic dubbed The Terrific. Terrific introduces Tou Kuan to his third rival, Thief Shih San-shou.

programme.title: The Blue and the Black
programme.desc: Set during the Japanese occupation in World War II, a young orphan Tang Qi falls in a love with a young man Chang. However, their love is filled with challenges, from family pressure to the turmoil of war. When Tang Qi was raped, she is expelled from home to become a nightclub singer and embarks on a journey of no return

programme.title: The Blue and the Black Part 2
programme.desc: Continuing from the first movie, Tang Qi ends her career as a nightclub singer and starts searching battle-scarred China for her lover Chang, who is now entangled with Japanese invaders, communist insurgents, and a warlord's beautiful daughter.

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: Finger of Doom
programme.desc: The protagonists are ex-swordmasters who now find joy in making umbrellas. They track down the evil Madame Kung Sun and her poisonous Finger of Doom, a unique supernatural power which allows her to transform normal, everyday people into horrifying zombies, and this is just the start of their mythical adventure against this zombie maker!

programme.title: Tiger Killer
programme.desc: Wu Song is appointed as chief constable after killing a tiger with his bare hands when drunk. The wife of his brother Wu Da Lang, seduces Wu Song but gets rejected by him, and engages in an affair with a rich man. They poison Wu Da Lang when he finds out about their affair. To avenge his brothers death, Wu Song kills both of them.

programme.title: Shaolin Mantis
programme.desc: The Emperor orders Feng to find proofs of Master Tians rebellion in his house. Feng falls in love with Tians granddaughter and marries her. When he finds the proofs and tries to leave with her, his wife is killed in the fight against Tian. Feng creates the mantis-style martial arts and vows to avenge her death.

programme.title: Madam White Snake
programme.desc: Linda Lin Dai is perfect as Pak Su-cheng, the stunning snake goddess who assumes a womanly form so that she can taste the pleasures of a human life! Pak seduces young scholar, Hsu Hsien when she recognises him as her saviour in another life 1,000 years ago. But when Buddhist monk Fa Hai finds out about the union, the pair is forced to split...

programme.title: The Bride Napping
programme.desc: A rich girl Yue Ying, together with her maid Chun Lan, encounter a poor scholar Bian Ji at a fte. Chun Lan realizes Yue Ying is in love with him, but mixes his identity with a bandit due to an old servants confusion, threatening the couples union. After a series of complications, misunderstandings and mismatches, Chun Lan finally saves the day.

programme.title: Life Gamble
programme.desc: Martial arts master Yu has retired for years but is invited to join force with another master Tao to fight against the four famous thieves and retrieve the stolen Dragon Jade. However, Taos real plan is to possess the treasure himself and kills Yu after he defeats the thieves...

programme.title: Temple Of The Red Lotus
programme.desc: A young guy Wu, heads off to the Dragon Valley to meet his childhood friend Lian Chu, who was promised to be his bride. When he arrives, he finds out that the family of his bride may not be an entirely honest bunch of people. Wu wishes to take Lian Chu with him, so he has no choice but to fight against her family

programme.title: The Heroic Ones
programme.desc: The story is set in the Tang Dynasty and David Chiang plays the 13th Prince, a powerful fighter whose prestigious status provokes jealously, leading to a gruesome family feud.

programme.title: Demon of the Lute
programme.desc: Lute demon Chin Mo has reappeared in the world to wreak havoc. Hsiao Feng Ling is ordered to help find a special bow and arrows that can counter the demon. Only Chiao Yin knows the whereabouts of the weapon. Hsiao and her classmate Old Naughty set out on an arduous journey to find Chiao. After overcoming many obstacles, they catch Chin Mo's man trying to snatch the bow and manage to stop him in time....

programme.title: My Dream Boat
programme.desc: This is a story about the complicated love relationships between a group of young friends who are entangled in a web of love and emotions.

programme.title: The Duel of the Century
programme.desc: A duel has been arranged at the Forbidden City between two formidable swordsmen of the martial world, Ye Gu Cheng and Xi Men Chui Xue. Lu Xiao Feng smells something fishy about the duel as the two swordsmen never met and do not have any conflicts. He decides to investigate more with Hua Man Lou, and eventually uncovers some hidden conspiracies

programme.title: The Shepherd Girl
programme.desc: In this musical drama, Hsiu Hsiu, a beautiful shepherd girl, falls in love with a handsome boatman Ta Lung. However, she cannot afford to marry him because of her fathers towering debt from gambling. To complicate the matter, a rival suitor promises to pay off all her father's debts on one condition: that Hsiu Hsiu marries him...

programme.title: Crocodile River
programme.desc: This story has a Romeo and Juliet flavour. Two families who hate each other live across the opposite sides of a river filled with crocodiles and do not bother to have a bridge built. Their respective children meet in university and fall in love, but have to find ways to be together and resolve the hatred between their families.

programme.title: Carry on Doctors and Nurses
programme.desc: At St. Morant Hospital, a harried but lovely administrator must deal with lusty interns, student nurses, a delirious surgeon, a dissection fiend, a criticizing Commissioner and gross negligence at regular intervals! This comedy is based on the hugely successful British Carry On! film series.

programme.title: The Rebel Intruders
programme.desc: Thousands of displaced refugees rush to the southern towns to avoid the civil war in north China. Three such young men trained with martial arts skills become sworn brothers, and accidentally got involved in the battle of the rebel leaders in town when they save a refugee girl. Can they fight back against the rebel gangs?

programme.title: A Maid From Heaven
programme.desc: The seventh daughter of the Jade Emperor is banished from heaven to live a mortal life as she is very mischievous. She falls in love with a young village lad Yong, who sold himself to work for the rich so as to bury his father. The goddess sisters help Yong to pay his debt so the lovebirds can be together. Is this going to end happily-ever-after?

programme.title: Return of the Sentimental Swordsman
programme.desc: One of Shaw Studios highest grossing movies ever, this is the story of Li Chin Huan, the renowned, charming and sentimental swordsman who must fight many opponents, including an evil Clan Chief, for a place in the martial arts world.

programme.title: The Daredevils
programme.desc: Corrupt general Wang Li assumes power by killing his superior. The son of the murdered superior befriends four street performers called The Venoms, and they help him take revenge by posing as government officials offering a peace token to the corrupt general. When Wang arrives at a warehouse, he is ambushed by the Venoms!

programme.title: Big Times for the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: Ah Niu finds a bag of jewels on the street and becomes rich. It is at this time that Uncle Zhou asks him to sign a contract to marry a girl, but it turns out to be a trap for Ah Niu to sell his house. In the end, Ah Niu becomes poor again

programme.title: Killers Five
programme.desc: The Dukes daughter has been kidnapped by the notorious Golden Dragon Hill bandits. A swordman named Yue Zhen Bei is assigned to save her, and expecting many dangers on the journey, Yue garners help from a group of good friends who are also kung fu masters.

programme.title: Hong Kong Nocturne
programme.desc: This joyous, raucous, & colorful tunefest showcases the little seen dancing talents of celebrated kung-fu swordswoman Cheng Pei-Pei, as one of 3 girls dancing their way to the top.

programme.title: The Shaolin Avengers
programme.desc: Hu seeks to avenge his father who is being killed by the White-Browed Hermit and his gang. However, he fails in his attempt and is saved by Fang Shi Yu, a youth from Shaolin whose parents are also killed by the same villains. They learn and master the advanced Shaolin style kung fu, before Fang leads Hu and the Shaolin fellows to fight the enemies.

programme.title: The Bride from Hell
programme.desc: A young business man marries a pretty and much sought-after young bride, not knowing that she carries the spirit of a girl raped by her uncle and murdered along with her parents. Justice must be done, and it ain't pretty!

programme.title: The Magnificent Swordsman
programme.desc: The Magnificent Swordsman centres on the hero who vows vengeance against evil bandits who killed his family when he was a child. The hero recruits several friends to help the peasants rid their village of marauding bandits, the leader of the band being the man who killed his family.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre
programme.desc: In the Yuan Dynasty, martial artists everywhere battle for the Heaven Sword and the Dragon Sabre, as only when these two powerful weapons combine can a secret be revealed to help one become the king of the martial arts world. As Zhang Wu Ji acquires the skills from Nine Yang Scriptures by chance, he is also embroiled in this lengthy battle.

programme.title: The Snake Prince
programme.desc: The Snake Prince lives on the Snake Mountain of Kwangsi with other snakes and they have lived peacefully with humans for a thousand years. All things change however, when the Snake Prince falls in love with one of the three beauties performing a sensual rain dance in the nearby village one day, and decides to marry her at all costs...

programme.title: The Love Eterne
programme.desc: Ying Tai disguises herself as a boy to go to school and falls hopelessly in love with her classmate, Shan Bo. After Shan Bo realizes her true identity, he proposes marriage to Ying Tai. However, they are kept apart as she is engaged to another man. Knowing Shan Bo died in despair, Ying Tai is in deep sorrow and kills herself at his grave.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma Ep75
programme.desc: The residents of Gokuldham Society encounter several adventures and misadventures as they navigate the ups and downs of life and overcome their struggles together in this animated series.

programme.title: Tarak Mehta Ka Chhota Chasma Ep76
programme.desc: The residents of Gokuldham Society encounter several adventures and misadventures as they navigate the ups and downs of life and overcome their struggles together in this animated series.

programme.title: Prince Jai Aur Dumdaar Viru Ep10
programme.desc: A prince and a commoner who are best friends keep having to thwart the plots of the prince's scheming, ambitious minister.

programme.title: Prince Jai Aur Dumdaar Viru Ep11
programme.desc: A prince and a commoner who are best friends keep having to thwart the plots of the prince's scheming, ambitious minister.

programme.title: Oh My Lallan Ep7
programme.desc: Lallan-a stray dog who lives around a house with 4 other Pets & sneaks into the house for food, water & shelter.The 4 pets' sole mission is to keep this stray dog away from them and the family

programme.title: Sab Jholmaal Hai Ep2
programme.desc: A hilarious animal chase comedy about the secret life and adventures of a dog, a parrot and twin bobcats living with Ms Katkar.

programme.title: Kicko & Super Speedo Ep19

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep23
programme.desc: New Hat, New Tag! / Furry Tail Ending - When Tag worries that she's no longer a "Go" dog, Lady Lydia helps her find a new persona by helping Tag try on a bunch of different hats. Luckily, when a runaway puppy needs to be wrangled, and only the speedy Tag can catch him, Tag realizes she was a Go dog all along. \ Sergeant Pooch reads Scooch, Tag and Kit a story book during their sleepover. But when the last pages are missing, the three kids work together to make up their own ending to the story.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep24
programme.desc: Bigpaw, Big Problems / Captain Scooch and Scally-Tag - Tag, Scooch and Kit think they found the perfect story for their newspaper: Bigpaw is in Pawston! But when they find out that Frank and Beans were lying to the town, they seek to uncover the truth and reveal it to everyone. \ When Sam Whippet sets up a pirate-themed race for the Race Cadets, pirate-loving Scooch takes on the role of captain. Tag struggles to take orders as first mate while helping Scooch navigate maritime obstacles and avoid the fearsome pirates.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep35
programme.desc: Hitting the Sky Note / Hug Fest - When Poppy discovers that Sky Toronto doesnt sing, she sets out to convince him that singing is the greatest joy in the world./Poppy shows Branch around his first Hug Fest, a Troll festival to celebrate hugs.

programme.title: Trolls: The Beat Goes On! Ep36
programme.desc: Chummy Sparklestone / Giggleyum - When the Funtime Factory stops producing one of their frosting flavors, Poppy sets out to create a replacement. But is her new flavor, Giggleyum too delicious?/During a Troll mystery party, Cooper has the role of detective. But when the party is over, Detective Cooper now Chummy Sparklestone refuses to break character, and hes causing problems around the village!

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep9
programme.desc: The Really Really Big Lie - When Julien concocts an elaborate lie, blaming a giant "mega-gecko" for ruining a young lemur's birthday party.

programme.title: All Hail King Julien Ep10
programme.desc: One More Cup - Julien finds a bag of coffee beans in the Cove of Wonders and gets the entire lemur community hooked on caffeine.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep14
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Tenuous Takedown of the Tyrannical Teachertrons - In the season opener, George and Harold have returned to school due to a technicality, but the school has been taken over by Melvin and a cyborg Melvin from the future! Their goal is to make the school extremely difficult by replacing all the teachers with Teachertron robots. Suffering under the new regime and without Mr. Krupp/Captain Underpants on hand to help, the boys hypnotize gym teacher Mr. Meaner and turn him into Sergeant Boxers to fight back.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep15
programme.desc: Captain Underpants and the Frantic Fury of the Fearsome Furculees - Tired of the Melvins ruling the school, the boys realize that they need Mr. Krupp to make the school at least bearable. Unfortunately, Krupp has run off to Ecuador to look for a fabled fountain. So the boys form the M.I.S.F.A.R.T.S. - Mega Incredible Search Force Adventure Rescue Team Squad - to travel to Ecuador and bring Krupp back, whether he wants it or not.

programme.title: The Adventures Of Puss In Boots Ep44
programme.desc: Breaking Good - When Dulcinea sets up a school to teach unruly thieves how to be good, Uli takes the idea too far and it's up to Puss to make San Lorenzo normal

programme.title: Not Quite Narwhal Ep18
programme.desc: Winkly Fest / Snow - When Pixie struggles to recreate an old tradition perfectly, the kids realize they can make their own traditions./ A story told by Chef J inspires Juniper to go in search of snow.

programme.title: Dew Drops Diaries Ep18
programme.desc: The Secret Ingredient / Delete That Dew! - When Harper is missing an ingredient to make her Moms favorite dessert on Mothers Day, Eden enlists the help of her fellow Dew Drops to do an emergency city-wide ingredient search! / When Marcus records a video of his inventions, Phoebe gets caught on camera and must erase the footage before Marcus sees, or her Dew Drop cover will be blown!

programme.title: Dragons: Rescue Riders Ep18
programme.desc: Summer Holiday - In need of some rest and relaxation, the Riders head out on vacation. But their supposedly perfect island getaway isn't quite what they hoped for.

programme.title: Go, Dog. Go! Ep4
programme.desc: Show Dog, Show \ Keys to Victory - Tag can't wait to show off her car at the car show. But when Cheddar Biscuit wants to come along and pick up her clown friends along the way, Tag is wary that Cheddar Biscuit will steal her thunder. \ The Not Yet Cadets can't wait to watch Sams big race. But when Sam loses his car key, he challenges the Not Yet Cadets to race around town to find it.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep42
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Senseless Torment Of The Space Toilet - Inspired by their favorite TV show, George and Harold along with Principal Krupp blast off to outer space, where an angry toilet awaits.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep43
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Abandoned Artifact Of The Absentee Aliens - After George and Harold learn the truth about their mission, Dupe Licitous enlists the entire crew in a quest to repair a rogue satellite.

programme.title: The Epic Tales of Captain Underpants Ep44
programme.desc: Captain Underpants And The Hazardous Hysteria Of The Hangry Hypnosinger - Everybody on the spaceship has been cryogenically frozen for three months everyone, that is, except Krupp, who's wide awake and happily in charge.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep14
programme.desc: When Lightning Strikes - The Vikings of Berk suspect the dragons may be causing lightning storms in the village.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep15
programme.desc: What Flies Beneath - Toothless encounters a rival from his past.

programme.title: Dragons: Riders of Berk Ep16
programme.desc: Defiant One - Hiccup and Snotlout struggle to find their way back from Outcast Island.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep68
programme.desc: Poompf! - Crispin Biscuits frames Boss and Tinas startup company for exploding baby Iggys favorite stuffed animal, and Tina is forced to the sidelines to avoid any more bad press. As Crispin expands his plan to burst all the plush toys in the neighborhood, Tina discovers she can stop this by breaking open and rewiring a single toy doll. Unfortunately that doll is Baby Corps current head honcho, Pull-String CEO Baby.

programme.title: Boss Baby: Back in the Crib Ep69
programme.desc: The Heat is On - On the hottest week of the year and a miserable time for babies, Boss and Tim infiltrates a country club with a very cool splash pad in order to find some way around their strict no-babies policy. Meanwhile, Banker Baby Benny visits the startup company to check on his investment.
